        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "<p>\\(x=\\frac{8+y}{2}\\), \\(y^2=\\frac{8}{3}x\\)</p>"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "<h4>metoda</h4>"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "<p>Podstawiamy \\(x\\) z pierwszego równania do drugiego:\n            \\[\n            y^2=\\frac{8}{3}\\cdot \\frac{8+y}{2}\n            \\]</p>"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "<h4>odpowiedź</h4>"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "body": "<p>Albo \\(x=6\\) i \\(y=4\\), albo \\(x=\\frac{8}{3}\\) i \\(x=-\\frac{8}{3}\\)</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
